    "dimensions": "120 cm × 87 cm",
    "location": "Private Collection",
    "description": "A young woman gazes into a crystal ball while a skull rests on the table beside her — the classic vanitas pairing of beauty and death. Waterhouse's rich, dark palette and the woman's absorbed expression create an atmosphere of intimate mystery.",
