    "description": "Rossetti depicts the legendary first wife of Adam as a beautiful, self-absorbed woman combing her luxuriant golden hair. Surrounded by roses and foxgloves, Lilith embodies dangerous beauty — a femme fatale who ensnares men with her physical allure.",
