    "year": 1854,
    "medium": "Oil on canvas",
    "dimensions": "125.5 cm × 59.8 cm",
    "location": "Keble College, Oxford",
    "description": "Christ stands at an overgrown door, knocking and holding a lantern — illustrating Revelation 3:20. The door has no external handle, signifying that it can only be opened from within. Hunt painted the nocturnal scene outdoors by moonlight and lantern to achieve authentic effects of light.",
